<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CSS BASICS</title>
    <style>
        .big{
            color: rgb(234, 111, 111);
            font-size: 20px;
            font-style: calc();
            font: bold;
            font: 500;
            border: 5px solid rgb(172, 172, 234);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .small{
            color: rgb(216, 142, 51);
            font-size: 20px;
            font-style: oblique;
            font: bolder;
            border: 5px solid rgb(43, 38, 38);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        *{
            background-image: url(https://picjumbo.com/wp-content/uploads/beautiful-nature-scenery-free-photo-2210x1473.jpg);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1 class="big red">CLASS EXAMPLE OF CSS</h1>
    <p class="green small">This is how we use Class Example</p>
    <p class="blue big">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Sapiente illo libero iusto? Quisquam quo veritatis praesentium ipsa, pariatur ab amet rem voluptate nisi non hic deleniti accusantium eveniet saepe maxime sequi voluptates aliquid quaerat, vero animi ipsam neque facere nulla reiciendis. Placeat harum quis veritatis?</p>
</body>
</html>
